all-academic.aspx|title=Herbert, Throckmorton named first-team Pac-12 All-Academic - GoDucks.com - The University of Oregon Official Athletics Web Site|website=GoDucks.com - The University of Oregon Official Athletics Web Site}}</ref>\n* Academic All American 1st Team <ref name=\"goducks.com\"/>\n* Offensive Team MVP (Oregon Team Award) <ref>{{cite web|url=https://goducks.com/news/2017/12/3/football-freeman-herbert-dye-among-honorees-at-awards-banquet.aspx?path=football|title=Freeman, Herbert, Dye Among Honorees At Awards Banquet - GoDucks.com - The University of Oregon Official Athletics Web Site|website=GoDucks.com - The University of Oregon Official Athletics Web Site}}</ref>\n\n====2018====\n* Google Cloud Academic All America 1st Team Member of the Year <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://academicallamerica.com/news/2018/12/10/2018-google-cloud-academic-all-america-ncaa-division-i-football-team-announced.aspx|title=2018 Google Cloud Academic All-America\u00ae NCAA Division I Football Team Announced|website=academicallamerica.com}}</ref>\n* Pac-12 All-Academic 1st team<ref name=\"2018 all-academic\" />\n* Skeie's Award (Oregon Team Award - Most Valuable Player) <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://goducks.com/news/2018/11/26/football-herbert-amadi-share-team-mvp-award.aspx|title=Herbert, Amadi Share Team MVP Award|website=University of Oregon Athletics}}</ref>\n\n====2019====\n* Pac-12 Offensive Player of the Week (Pac-12 Coaches) \u2013 October 21, 2019 <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pac-12.com/videos/oregons-justin-herbert-named-pac-12-offensive-player-week-after-4-touchdown-performance|title=Oregon's Justin Herbert named Pac-12 Offensive Player of the Week after 4-touchdown performance|website=Pac-12}}</ref>\n* [[William V. Campbell Trophy]]{{cn|date=January 2020}}\n\n====2020====\n*[[2020 Rose Bowl|Rose Bowl]] Offensive MVP{{cn|date=January 2020}}\n\n==Professional career==\n{{NFL predraft\n|    height ft = 6\n|    height in = 6\u00bc\n|       weight = 236\n|         dash = 4.6